        <mxCell id="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-4" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 110%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lexend&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Explain the concept of &quot;characteristic scale&quot; in blob detection. How is it determined using the NLoG operator?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=22;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontFamily=Mina;arcSize=5;hachureGap=4;align=left;spacingRight=5;fontStyle=0;fillStyle=hachure;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=29;spacingBottom=0;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DADLaM%2BDisplay;fontColor=#333333;" parent="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-3" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="26.61" width="763.39" height="55" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-5" value="1" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;strokeWidth=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#666666;fontFamily=Mina;fontStyle=1;fontSize=20;spacingTop=3;fontColor=#333333;rounded=1;fillStyle=hachure;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=0;spacingBottom=3;arcSize=14;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DADLaM%2BDisplay;" parent="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-3" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry width="55.5" height="55.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-6" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(230, 230, 230);&quot;&gt;1.0&lt;/font&gt;" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=#FFF2CC99;" parent="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="790" y="5.5" width="33" height="14.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="aJxTqxu9sF447ppHcIcN-0" value="" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/jpeg,;clipPath=inset(0% 0% 2.16% 0% round 5%);" parent="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="151.34" y="1690" width="520.33" height="432.74111666666664" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="QcRXOSVlALn9-Xd7sjj--0" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;is the scale (`\sigma` value) at which the &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;`\sigma`-NLoG&lt;/font&gt; response reach to local maximum at the blob&#39;s center.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;As `\sigma` increases, the response for a blob &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;rises, peaks, then falls&lt;/font&gt;. `\sigma` at &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;peak is approximate fit to the blob&#39;s width&lt;/font&gt; and becomes characteristic scale.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeWidth=0.5;fillColor=#FFF2CC;strokeColor=#582826;container=0;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;fontFamily=Fustat;spacingLeft=2;align=left;spacingTop=0;" parent="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="48" y="170" width="731" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OS0vPkaLfSEMT8pTKuvR-0" value="&lt;div style=&quot;direction: rtl;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Aviny&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;الـ characteristic scale هو الـ `\sigma`&amp;nbsp;اللي عنده الـ blob يظهر بأوضح شكل مع الـ NLoG.&lt;br&gt;يعني وإنت بتكبر الـ scale، الاستجابة تعلى شوية لحد ما توصل لأعلى قيمة، وبعدها تقل، فالـ peak ده يمثل الحجم الحقيقي للـ blob.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=right;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Mina;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#333333;" parent="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="490" y="223" width="288.14" height="26" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OS0vPkaLfSEMT8pTKuvR-1" value="" style="group" parent="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-1" vertex="1" connectable="0">
          <mxGeometry x="19" y="260" width="790" height="55.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OS0vPkaLfSEMT8pTKuvR-2" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 110%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lexend&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Describe&lt;/font&gt; the Difference of Gaussian (DoG) approximation. &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;Why &lt;/font&gt;is it used in SIFT instead of directly computing the NLoG?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=22;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontFamily=Mina;arcSize=5;hachureGap=4;align=left;spacingRight=5;fontStyle=0;fillStyle=hachure;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=29;spacingBottom=0;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DADLaM%2BDisplay;fontColor=#333333;" parent="OS0vPkaLfSEMT8pTKuvR-1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="26.61" width="763.39" height="55" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OS0vPkaLfSEMT8pTKuvR-3" value="2" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;strokeWidth=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#666666;fontFamily=Mina;fontStyle=1;fontSize=20;spacingTop=3;fontColor=#333333;rounded=1;fillStyle=hachure;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=0;spacingBottom=3;arcSize=14;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DADLaM%2BDisplay;" parent="OS0vPkaLfSEMT8pTKuvR-1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry width="55.5" height="55.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OS0vPkaLfSEMT8pTKuvR-4" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;*&lt;/font&gt;DoG approximates the NLoG. It is &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;computed by subtracting images in the scale space&lt;/font&gt; `\text{DoG} = S(x, y, \sigma_k) - S(x, y, \sigma_{k-1})`&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;*&lt;/font&gt;because it uses &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;less computation&lt;/font&gt; - just image &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;subtractions instead of&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Laplacian convolutions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeWidth=0.5;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#6C4E00;container=0;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;fontFamily=Fustat;spacingLeft=2;align=left;spacingTop=0;" parent="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="48.5" y="330" width="731" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OS0vPkaLfSEMT8pTKuvR-5" value="&lt;div style=&quot;direction: rtl;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Aviny&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;الـ DoG بيطلع نتيجة شبه الـ NLoG عن طريق طرح صورتين من بعض بدل حساب Laplacian كله كل مرة.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;SIFT بيستخدمه لأنه أسرع وأوفر استهلاك موارد.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=right;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Mina;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#333333;" parent="KfrxztiE6OfKk03DvFlC-1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="490" y="380" width="288.14" height="26" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
