        <mxCell id="2VT8IgdAOZ9plX4UFobo-17" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot; face=&quot;Aviny&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;الـ Non-Maximal Suppression بيهتم بأقوى edge أو corner القيم&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(77, 77, 77), rgb(171, 171, 171));&quot;&gt;ويشيل القيم الأضعف حواليها.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(77, 77, 77), rgb(171, 171, 171));&quot;&gt;مهم في الـ Harris، عشان القيم بتبقي عالية عند الـ corners و حواليه فعايز اقلل العدد ده لحد ما اوصل للـ corner بس.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=right;textDirection=rtl;verticalAlign=middle;horizontal=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;rounded=0;glass=0;shadow=0;arcSize=6;spacingLeft=2;fontSize=10;fontColor=#4D4D4D;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="447" y="2764" width="315.89" height="16" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="2VT8IgdAOZ9plX4UFobo-18" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;- because it consists of &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 153);&quot;&gt;fast, random intensity changes&lt;/font&gt;,&amp;nbsp; which this is a &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 153);&quot;&gt;target of edge detector&lt;/font&gt; so it &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 153);&quot;&gt;cause many false edges&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;- solution is to &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 153);&quot;&gt;smooth image&lt;/font&gt; to reduce noise (Gaussian) before apply derivative operator or &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 153);&quot;&gt;convolve a derivative of Gaussian&lt;/font&gt; directly.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeWidth=0.5;fillColor=#FFF2CC;strokeColor=#582826;container=0;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;fontFamily=Fustat;spacingLeft=2;align=left;spacingTop=-24;" vertex="1" parent="1">
