        <mxCell id="ucWEhtidr9BQ_HSIXQms-4" value="1" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;strokeWidth=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#666666;fontFamily=Mina;fontStyle=1;fontSize=20;spacingTop=3;fontColor=#333333;rounded=1;fillStyle=hachure;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=0;spacingBottom=3;arcSize=14;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DADLaM%2BDisplay;" vertex="1" parent="ucWEhtidr9BQ_HSIXQms-2">
          <mxGeometry width="55.5" height="55.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ucWEhtidr9BQ_HSIXQms-6" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;A point (`x_i, y_i`) in image space maps to a line `c=-mx_i+y_i` in (`m, c`) parameter space. A line in image&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;space (with same `m, c`) maps to a point in parameter space.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;This duality allows voting: each image point&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;votes for all possible lines on it, and intersections in parameter space on lines&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;in image space.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeWidth=0.5;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#564260;container=0;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;fontFamily=Fustat;spacingLeft=2;align=left;spacingTop=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="50.5" y="3413" width="731" height="63" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ucWEhtidr9BQ_HSIXQms-7" value="" style="group" vertex="1" connectable="0" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="21" y="3334" width="790" height="55.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ucWEhtidr9BQ_HSIXQms-8" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 110%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lexend&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Explain the duality between &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;image space&lt;/font&gt; and &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;parameter space&lt;/font&gt; in the Hough transform for line detection using the (`m, c`) parameterization. How does a point in image space map to parameter space, and vice versa?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=22;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontFamily=Mina;arcSize=5;hachureGap=4;align=left;spacingRight=5;fontStyle=0;fillStyle=hachure;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=29;spacingBottom=0;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DADLaM%2BDisplay;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="ucWEhtidr9BQ_HSIXQms-7">
