        <mxCell id="ucWEhtidr9BQ_HSIXQms-13" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;(`m, c`) cannot represent vertical lines (`m=\infty`) and can&#39;t accumulate arrays. (`\rho, \infty`) has&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;finite ranges (`0\le\theta&amp;lt;\pi`), (`\rho` bounded by image diagonal), but now can represent all lines including vertical lines.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeWidth=0.5;fillColor=#FFF2CC;strokeColor=#582826;container=0;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;fontFamily=Fustat;spacingLeft=2;align=left;spacingTop=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
