        <mxCell id="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-1" value="Rev. Sheet #4" style="shape=hexagon;perimeter=hexagonPerimeter2;whiteSpace=wrap;fixedSize=1;size=16;fontFamily=ADLaM Display;fontSize=20;strokeWidth=1;align=center;spacingLeft=0;spacingBottom=4;fillStyle=hachure;fontStyle=1;rounded=1;arcSize=50;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DADLaM%2BDisplay;fillColor=#FFEBF1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="24" y="4690" width="780" height="48" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-2" value="" style="group" vertex="1" connectable="0" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="23" y="4763" width="790" height="55.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-3" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 110%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lexend&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Explain the concept of &quot;characteristic scale&quot; in blob detection. How is it determined using the NLoG operator?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=22;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontFamily=Mina;arcSize=5;hachureGap=4;align=left;spacingRight=5;fontStyle=0;fillStyle=hachure;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=29;spacingBottom=0;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DADLaM%2BDisplay;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-2">
          <mxGeometry x="26.61" width="763.39" height="55" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-4" value="1" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;strokeWidth=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#666666;fontFamily=Mina;fontStyle=1;fontSize=20;spacingTop=3;fontColor=#333333;rounded=1;fillStyle=hachure;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=0;spacingBottom=3;arcSize=14;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DADLaM%2BDisplay;" vertex="1" parent="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-2">
          <mxGeometry width="55.5" height="55.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-5" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;is the scale (`\sigma` value) at which the &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;`\sigma`-NLoG&lt;/font&gt; response reach to local maximum at the blob&#39;s center.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;As `\sigma` increases, the response for a blob &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;rises, peaks, then falls&lt;/font&gt;. `\sigma` at &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;peak is approximate fit to the blob&#39;s width&lt;/font&gt; and becomes characteristic scale.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeWidth=0.5;fillColor=#FFF2CC;strokeColor=#582826;container=0;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;fontFamily=Fustat;spacingLeft=2;align=left;spacingTop=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="52" y="4840" width="731" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-6" value="&lt;div style=&quot;direction: rtl;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Aviny&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;الـ characteristic scale هو الـ `\sigma`&amp;nbsp;اللي عنده الـ blob يظهر بأوضح شكل مع الـ NLoG.&lt;br&gt;يعني وإنت بتكبر الـ scale، الاستجابة تعلى شوية لحد ما توصل لأعلى قيمة، وبعدها تقل، فالـ peak ده يمثل الحجم الحقيقي للـ blob.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=right;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Mina;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="494" y="4893" width="288.14" height="26" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-7" value="" style="group" vertex="1" connectable="0" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="23" y="4930" width="790" height="55.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-8" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 110%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Lexend&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Describe&lt;/font&gt; the Difference of Gaussian (DoG) approximation. &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;Why &lt;/font&gt;is it used in SIFT instead of directly computing the NLoG?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=22;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontFamily=Mina;arcSize=5;hachureGap=4;align=left;spacingRight=5;fontStyle=0;fillStyle=hachure;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=29;spacingBottom=0;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DADLaM%2BDisplay;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-7">
          <mxGeometry x="26.61" width="763.39" height="55" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-9" value="2" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;strokeWidth=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#666666;fontFamily=Mina;fontStyle=1;fontSize=20;spacingTop=3;fontColor=#333333;rounded=1;fillStyle=hachure;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=0;spacingBottom=3;arcSize=14;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DADLaM%2BDisplay;" vertex="1" parent="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-7">
          <mxGeometry width="55.5" height="55.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-10" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;*&lt;/font&gt;DoG approximates the NLoG. It is &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;computed by subtracting images in the scale space&lt;/font&gt; `\text{DoG} = S(x, y, \sigma_k) - S(x, y, \sigma_{k-1})`&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;*&lt;/font&gt;because it uses &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;less computation&lt;/font&gt; - just image &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;subtractions instead of&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Laplacian convolutions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeWidth=0.5;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#6C4E00;container=0;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;fontFamily=Fustat;spacingLeft=2;align=left;spacingTop=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="52.5" y="5000" width="731" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="yhAgFun6bCtzyW4o2Wya-11" value="&lt;div style=&quot;direction: rtl;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Aviny&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;الـ DoG بيطلع نتيجة شبه الـ NLoG عن طريق طرح صورتين من بعض بدل حساب Laplacian كله كل مرة.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;SIFT بيستخدمه لأنه أسرع وأوفر استهلاك موارد.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=right;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Mina;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="494" y="5050" width="288.14" height="26" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
